    "text": "A 30-year-old woman with asthma visits her GP for a routine check-up. She is currently using a metered dose inhaler (MDI) containing salbutamol as a reliever and a MDI containing fluticasone and salmeterol as a preventer. She has good asthma control and no adverse effects from her inhalers. She expresses concern about the environmental impact of her inhalers\r\n\r\nAn extract from the NHS website has been provided for you.",
