    "why": "Determine the total daily morphine equivalent dose in mg/day. In this case, it is 30mg x 2 + 5mg x 5 = 85 mg/day.\r\nChoose the nearest available patch strength and frequency of application.\r\nTherefore, the most appropriate initial dose of buprenorphine patches for this patient is 35 micrograms/hour.",
